{"tid":1711132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"所有香港大學/大專院校應立即無限期停課 以保障學生安全","createTime":"2019-11-12T10:10:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T10:26:24.000Z","uid":51039,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7424d09d3d63b2f8b5466e92152c8bd4a810f88a","tid":1711132,"uid":51039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:10:08.000Z","msg":"中大城大理大等等都已被恐怖分子攻擊<br />\n難保其他八大以及大專院校係未來會成為攻擊目標<br />\n所有大學/大專院校必須立即停課<br />\n保護學生<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">否則就是置學生性命於不顧</span></span><br />\n各大學生會，屬會，學生個人，甚至家長等等<br />\n立即email 俾自己學校！"},{"pid":"f45fd75404a9a4e9d0751719efaeb5ae63e8e5d2","tid":1711132,"uid":51039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:12:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a66bd725ada561176f957205e71abc5e8508a0","tid":1711132,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:12:09.000Z","msg":"!!!!!中大告急，中大告急!!!!!<br />\n出唔到去嘅人幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入去 <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=9CaroZtPfqcCLVRp0XVEkRphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=ae2a6124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務<br />\n<br />\n今日Task分類<br />\n/task1: 中環罷工<br />\n/task2: 其他中國同香港議題<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">/task3: </span></span>！！！中大！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Rt + like + reply </span><br />\n<br />\n幫推<br />\n(突發）幫手救中大（twitter戰線）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1710885\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1710885</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2a5d9f03ff22efb378a169b881e00d15945a710e","tid":1711132,"uid":51039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-1